The Qt Design Studio 2.0.0 release contains bug fixes and new features.

General
   * Integrated user statistics (QDS-3140)
   * Integrated crash reporter (QDS-3228)
   * Implemented locking of items (QDS-2915)
   * Implemented logical NOT in binding editor (QDS-2872)
   * Added technical preview for Figma bridge
   * Changed how 2D effects work (QDS-2948)
   * Added Logic Helpers (QDS-2949)

Documentation
   * Updated Qt Design Studio Manual to version 2.0.0
   * Added documentation for most commonly-used QML types (QDS-3229)
   * Updated documentation about 2D effects (QDS-3230)
   * Added documentation for Figma bridge

Curve Editor
   * Improved mouse pad support on macOS

Form Editor
   * Improved mouse pad support on macOS (QDS-2943)

Property Editor
   * Improved drag editing in Properties (QDS-2371)
   * Added easier way to start editing component (QDS-2358)
   * Improved template generation (QDS-3062)

Qt for MCUs
   * Fixed showing items not available for Qt for MCUs

Navigator
   * Implemented navigator preview for components, images, textures, materials and models (QDS-2750)
   * Added option to reverse order (QDS-2773)
   * Updated styling of navigator delegates

Item Library
  * Added component preview to item library (QDS-3005)

Wizards
   * Adjusted supported resolutions for MCU wizards

Asset Importer
   * Fixed merging of MouseAreas (QDS-1587)
   * Fixed merging of bindings (QDS-2555)

Asset Exporter
   * Added an option to generate PSD file for each component we export (QDS-3107)
   * Set the default DPI to 72 (QDS-2991)

Qt Bridge for Adobe Photoshop
   * Fixed multiline export (QDS-2556)
   * Fixed child layers under group which exported to Controls (QDS-2535)
   * Added option to export text items as image (QDS-1137)
   * Fixed error with documents without Artboards
   * Fixed that data update on selection change was not optimized
   * Updated font matching algorithm
   * Fixed layer size of Text layer import
   * Fixed PSD generation issues:
       * Fixed initialization errors
       * Fixed document cleanup
       * Line height is respected
       * DPI settings are considered

Qt Bridge for Sketch:
   * Added option to export text items as image (QDS-1137)
   * Fixed stale data on layer selection.

QML Puppet
   * Added support for Qt 6

3D View
   * Added support for Qt 6 based qml2puppet
